- Custom annotations are created by defining a class and using @ to apply the annotation. Example:

      ```dart
      class MyAnnotation {
        final String description;

        const MyAnnotation(this.description);
      }

      @MyAnnotation('This is a custom annotation')
      class MyClass {}
      ```

